{"tid":633083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺街邊啲健身狗好撚柒煩","createTime":"2018-04-18T03:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T15:12:52.000Z","uid":110464,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3298d0c12a835c65fd93928c3d7f26b7010ab98c","tid":633083,"uid":110464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚開錯台，所以今日開返喺呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次會分開出，驚太密好難睇 <br />\n原POST: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/632550/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/632550/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n相信唔少人都試過喺條街俾健身狗逗，通常都係比張卡你然後話「最後一個啦求下你啦」、「趕住放飯/收工啊」，而大家都會因為做下好心而接咗張卡，再俾人帶咗上去。<br />\n<br />\n我明白唔少人都會覺得只係自己衰耳仔軟/蠢/ON9，好多人都係遭遇呢啲經歷而冇出聲。唔係個個都好似連登仔咁勁，反而本身可能係好怕事，所以希望呢個post可以幫到呢啲人。<br />\n<br />\n其實就算真係當事人笨柒，都唔代表間健身中心手法係正確。特別有啲上晒新聞嘅案例，即使你有興趣做GYM，你都可以認真思考下係咪真係去個間做，搵多啲相關資訊先，保障自己好重要。<br />\n成個POST都係聽啲親朋好友、上消委會搵資訊，所以大家有更多資訊可以提供就更好！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（一）\t大概內容<br />\n通常佢都係搵啲比較後生少少，同埋個樣冇咁惡嘅人（越毒越好），至於睇得出本身操開ＧＹＭ/中年個啲佢就通常唔會搵架啦。<br />\n<br />\n我諗有啲人未去過，喺到簡單講講上去之後大概會點。<br />\n首先佢會同你傾下計先，然後搵啲共同興趣乜乜乜，即係Ｒ水吹扮熟。跟住就可能會問你拎啲證件，然後帶你去磅重，分析下邊到肥邊到瘦咁啦，之後就會開始SELL你，話你要增肌/減肥等等啦，不斷講你啲缺點。<br />\n<br />\n佢一開始唔會同你講錢住，佢會先問你時間、屋企地址等等，最後先會問你BUDGET。之後佢就會不斷撳低價錢，話已經特登幫你搞咗個好平嘅價，可能仲平過你本來Budget 。跟住就會話今日係最後一日，只有今日先有優惠，總之就係sell到你應承為止。<br />\n<br />\n（價錢方面，我身邊有啲人可能大家都係報兩年，但係價錢唔同，如果你係本身有興趣上去玩，咁你要小心地同佢討論價錢啦）<br />\n<br />\n而佢簽約前同簽約後，都會叫你錄音，證明晒你係知道佢講緊啲咩嘅。但之後見過有巴打講其實冇錄到，只係嚇下，呢層我都唔太SURE，但我諗假設佢有先隱陣啲。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢會叫健身教練帶你去試下啲機，呢個地方要留心，下面（三）會再詳細講。<br />\n試完機之後就會SELL埋你健身教練PLAN，不過因為費用都貴，所以通常簽完約都唔會再想JOIN，我自己都唔太清楚呢方面。"},{"pid":"d81e22b690fb1c2b8cb5dd12ce8513dce2de6890","tid":633083,"uid":135313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"係男人嘅就去康文操下佢<br />\n以家出到街冇sales埋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df25170faa4d317fc2c576a1d67a975fe07c53","tid":633083,"uid":24121,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95e7d6e820492e26bbce0e1a2f2613e5072f802e","tid":633083,"uid":15011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健身狗死全家"},{"pid":"f6b85dda5cf32cde26021b6e617340aadc4c3d8b","tid":633083,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"如果係女SALES"},{"pid":"098ee88ad42ad205677aedac1a573ed08b7c975b","tid":633083,"uid":110464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"（二）注意事項<br />\n有幾樣野係你要特別留意，尤其係對健身完全冇興趣但易心軟嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n1.\t唔好隨意接傳單<br />\n呢個唔洗多講，就算接咗都即刻塞返俾佢，仲可以送返啲四字真言俾佢。<br />\n<br />\n2.\t＊上到去唔好隨意拎證件出嚟<br />\n通常上到去都會叫你拎身份證或者其他證件，但記住唔好俾，你唔知佢拎嚟做咩，亦都唔知佢會唔會扣起你張卡。如果你本身冇興趣但又上咗去，基本上佢一叫你俾卡你就即走啦！<br />\n<br />\n2011 07 16<br />\n健身中心扣身份證硬銷<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110716/15436861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110716%2F15436861&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cb9bd9c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110716%2F15436861&h=8192852c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110716/15436861</a><br />\n2015 12 29<br />\n健身中心職員誘騙智障男入會買堂 涉款逾百萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151229/54587972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151229%2F54587972&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2a820557\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20151229%2F54587972&h=d8428285\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20151229/54587972</a><br />\n<br />\n　　＊唔好透露自己有信用卡<br />\n　　　呢樣野好重要，一旦自己俾佢知你有信用卡咁就係惡夢嘅開始！！！佢地會不斷疲勞轟炸你幾個鐘，然後同你講可以分期俾錢。所謂嘅分期俾錢，即係過咗數，然後叫你自己去銀行申請。假設你一個月俾３００蚊，總共兩年，即係７２００蚊。而分期付款唔係講緊逐個月收三百蚊，而係佢過晒７２００蚊，你再去銀行申請分期付款，至於申請分期付款嘅手續費就應該間間銀行唔同。　<br />\n　　　同埋分期付款都講緊每月定期支出，冇穩定工作嘅人要特別諗清楚啊！<br />\n<br />\n　　＊望清楚俾咗幾多錢<br />\n　　呢個唔洗多講，睇清楚機上面嘅銀碼，如果死都唔俾你睇你就千其唔好入密碼，如果你最後點都睇唔到，咁唔該睇清你份約同收據，正常收據都會寫咗你俾幾錢。"},{"pid":"f3f186164357d3af25eea9528a1c6b30a83be658","tid":633083,"uid":48234,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b4df25170faa4d317fc2c576a1d67a975fe07c53","tid":633083,"uid":24121,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z4wqgu3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ4wqgu3.gif&h=25397f98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5216d64039deee92e9b30df0fd76656a6306721","tid":633083,"uid":66736,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"咁都要人教不如死撚左佢算"},{"pid":"61a1c0e02774a6ef43c01bd2451e2d8983162e75","tid":633083,"uid":110840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"以前就係衰好心，俾之前執左笠個間大型連鎖gym氹左上去，幫佢拎最後一張coupon，話要簽d野先攞得<br />\n上到去狂sell我，又度高磅重，周圍參觀，又係話幫我R到個平價plan俾我<br />\nsell左我2個鐘，隔離枱個毒毒俾個女sales sell到就黎簽約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我一直堅持唔join，仲好坦白講: 我真係諗住好心幫你，完全無諗過join，又話有fd等緊我，先肯放我走"},{"pid":"31d1c5bf0350b3333fe3414957fe78e945debae6","tid":633083,"uid":110840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61a1c0e02774a6ef43c01bd2451e2d8983162e75","tid":633083,"uid":110840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"以前就係衰好心，俾之前執左笠個間大型連鎖gym氹左上去，幫佢拎最後一張coupon，話要簽d野先攞得<br />\n上到去狂sell我，又度高磅重，周圍參觀，又係話幫我R到個平價plan俾我<br />\nsell左我2個鐘，隔離枱個毒毒俾個女sales sell到就黎簽約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我一直堅持唔join，仲好坦白講: 我真係諗住好心幫你，完全無諗過join，又話有fd等緊我，先肯放我走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"好在我話自己乜卡都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaec1d66f58bbd7a88ff1a6bbbbf409737ec4fc","tid":633083,"uid":110464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"（三）\t<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">取消會籍 ***********（重要！！！！）</span></span></span></strong><br />\n健身中心銷售手法詬病未除　消費者慎防誤墮預繳陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/news/press/480/fitness-centres.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumer.org.hk%2Fws_chi%2Fnews%2Fpress%2F480%2Ffitness-centres.html&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dbf2242f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consumer.org.hk/ws_chi/news/press/480/fitness-centres.html</a><br />\n<br />\n簽約嘅時候，好多時佢會好快拎走份約，又或者係有啲新聞講話佢會遮住條款，睇上面消委會嘅調查，更加會有啲拒絕俾你睇條款，所以未睇晒/冇得睇都唔好簽。<br />\n對於CANCEL會籍，間間有唔同做法，有啲係唔俾退會；有啲係可以提早退，但至少履行一半合約期同埋有手續費；有啲係要有醫生證明文件（好似大肚或整親），甚至你提供咗都可能要收手續費。<br />\n<br />\n有一啲就會聲稱有五日或者七日冷靜期/退款保證，但有部份規定要「未享用過佢服務」，或「只適用於首次登記嘅會員」。又或者冷靜期內取消合約，要先扣除入會費同行政費。<br />\n（冷靜期即係合期限限內可以無條件退貨，政府而家仲未正式立法規定要有，我第六部份會講少少）<br />\n<br />\n而承接返第一部份，有啲有冷靜期嘅公司，個前提可能係規定咗「未享用過佢嘅服務」。不過好似我第一部份咁講，簽約後佢會叫教練帶你「試玩下」，事後同你講「一用咗就冇冷靜期」，而佢事前亦都冇同我講過有冷靜期呢樣野。亦見過有啲人掂咗部機都當係享用佢地服務，亦有用咗會員證試入一次就等於享用咗服務。所以呢方面真係要好小心！！！！！<br />\n冷靜期係退唔退到款嘅關鍵，喺簽合約個陣如果見到呢個字，一定要問到一清二楚！！！！"},{"pid":"fcfa2487d3014fbae5686f88ed9d91eac1b98c9a","tid":633083,"uid":129741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"黃埔個d好q煩"},{"pid":"814e441c4bdf10a65d97641cbafa19c20ae8c2bc","tid":633083,"uid":146009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"見到啲瘦到成條柴咁既仲好意思sale<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢一啲說服力都冇 都唔間公司念乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab64149f56f1e9b3ab6852200e6dbcbc5d151fe","tid":633083,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"扮基同佢講執返劑就上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18230a83e16a1e6248d49abd0963d4dd7bcc721","tid":633083,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"影佢地相放上來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cd7d529e8ce666f754069cf543f8f3e50b376c","tid":633083,"uid":110464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"（四）\t相關條例<br />\n做得健身個班人未必知香港有咩條例，所以學識保障自己真係好重要，我簡單列幾條出嚟當係旁身之用，因為字數太多所以我放埋條LINK唔引文啦。<br />\n＊香港法例第362章《商品說明條例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap362!zh-Hant-HK@2014-12-05T00:00:00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap362%21zh-Hant-HK%402014-12-05T00%3A00%3A00&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=798aa8f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap362!zh-Hant-HK@2014-12-05T00:00:00</a><br />\n2B部　13E.　誤導性遺漏<br />\n13F. 具威嚇性的營業行為<br />\n　　＊服務提供（隱含條款）條例<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/457/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F457%2F&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a7a34e05\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/457/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkclic.org/tc/topics/consumer_complaints/consumer_contracts/q1.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkclic.org%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2Fconsumer_complaints%2Fconsumer_contracts%2Fq1.shtm&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=df303994\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkclic.org/tc/topics/consumer_complaints/consumer_contracts/q1.shtm</a>l<br />\n<br />\n（五）上咗去點走佬好？<br />\n　　一、就咁走，唔撚理佢，鍾意嘅可以屌佢幾句<br />\n　　二、佢唔俾你走或者扣卡，最緊要惡撚過佢，佢始終都只係SALES，再唔係就報警，安全最緊要。<br />\n　　三、話自己未夠十八歲（未俾身份證嘅話），然後話要問監護人；<br />\n　　　　話自己冇信用卡或者銀行冇錢，返屋企諗諗先。<br />\n最緊要嘅係，有咩事就報警啦！！！！！作為消費者，麻煩你睇清楚諗清楚，保障自己最緊要呀！！！！如果姑息只會令佢地嘅手法更加猖狂架咋。<br />\n<br />\n報之前諗清楚<br />\n　　一、值得咩？？？講真又唔係少錢，辛苦賺返嚟值得俾人講兩個講就DUM錢落去？<br />\n　　二、有時間咩？真係想報？講真佢地係長期合約，報咗真係有恆心上？唔好俾人SELL 下就以為自己就真係有興趣啊！<br />\n　　三、間公司值得支持？呢樣唔多講，太多例子。諗清楚呢間公司係咪真係值得你支持同信賴。<br />\n　　四、不過如果你真係好得閒意志好堅定，可以上去做下免費脂肪檢測，又可以阻止佢Ｒ下一個客人。若不幸俾人動搖咗，即刻GOOGLE下啲人點屌&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"813bbb094aef9bbe12335413ed5e046ba597d407","tid":633083,"uid":28503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"D健身狗多數都鐘意搵d毒撚、肥仔肥妹笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有返咁上下身型佢地都識知難而退<br />\n上次同個消防fd出街 見佢一野撞開個肥仔健身狗<br />\n個肥仔敢怒不敢言個樣幾趣緻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d43b2dd8e63e20dfe73e7bf4500aa9fbaf3be2","tid":633083,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"唔理佢直行直過就得"},{"pid":"c2d86e0a73765dbcc365a2fe57748ede8ffba2f3","tid":633083,"uid":110464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"（六）\t更多資訊<br />\n<br />\n政府做緊乜？　　<br />\n<br />\n　　其實香港早喺2010年已經喺修訂《商品說明條例》個陣，有討論過「消費合約強制設立冷靜期及相關措施」，將範圍擴展到所有合約期達半年以上嘅預繳式消費，不過因為商家佬反對，最終政府都係跪低咗！<br />\n<br />\n　　　　過咗幾年後，再有議員建議討論，但政府就話做研究先<br />\n／／政府亦會觀察《商品說明條例》在處理不良營商手法方面的成效， 以及社會人士對實施強制性冷靜期的意見。此外，政府已向消費者 委員會提供資源，進行有關冷靜期的研究， 預料有關研究將 在 2017 年完成。／／<br />\n<br />\n　　　　亦將冷靜期呢項議題列入經發局嘅2017-2018待議事項，不過正式討論時間仲係待定，因為要等埋個研究。<br />\n　　　　而消委個網就話研究今年內先會發佈，到時大家多多留意下啦！<br />\n<br />\n經發局待議事項一覽<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/panels/edev/papers/edev20180122cb4-486-1-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fedev%2Fpapers%2Fedev20180122cb4-486-1-c.pdf&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b38cd234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/panels/edev/papers/edev20180122cb4-486-1-c.pdf</a><br />\n[/url]資料摘要，可以睇到唔同地方嘅規管，除咗冷靜期仲有啲對消費者嘅保障，好似係限定合約期限等等<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/1617in19-consumer-protection-for-prepaid-services-contracts-20171009-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fresearch-publications%2Fchinese%2F1617in19-consumer-protection-for-prepaid-services-contracts-20171009-c.pdf&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=42ad4a25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/1617in19-consumer-protection-for-prepaid-services-contracts-20171009-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有其他資料都可以補充！<br />\n<br />\n2015 11 10<br />\nCalifornia健身教練　呃客140萬買堂 騙14萬佣金　累一受害人破產<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151110/19366910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151110%2F19366910&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c3f1f165\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151110%2F19366910&h=2990d3ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151110/19366910</a><br />\n<br />\n2017 04 12<br />\n健身會籍騙案 經理拍枱阻少女報警<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170412/19988101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170412%2F19988101&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e31dbdc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170412%2F19988101&h=b90bf671\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170412/19988101</a><br />\n<br />\n2017 01 02<br />\n被指擅碌客卡$10萬　FFG健身中心稱徹查<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170102/bkn-20170102115056040-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170102%2Fbkn-20170102115056040-0102_00822_001.html&d=iV%2BIcVmtk%2BfJ2CliG5mnCJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9be7f836\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170102/bkn-20170102115056040-0102_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，如果大家好想好想退錢，就上去同佢地傾，最緊要態度夠強硬，搵定消委、海關嘅電話。"},{"pid":"6b7bd913860787bceb984e46153fafff4c05a3ae","tid":633083,"uid":1022,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fe14f05df413811625679bfcacec5cf5b043f1","tid":633083,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"774e6b36a67cc5776114be59e3d906f9450d9cf2","tid":633083,"uid":15011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a58f42ad9fd4acc94ec79ffe423f2864991a52","tid":633083,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf39c9e8fad31baf4fbe541470477c6c9f3587a4","tid":633083,"uid":137704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4df25170faa4d317fc2c576a1d67a975fe07c53","tid":633083,"uid":24121,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"},{"pid":"83e1b82005869032ded26abb18499872e3ac74d3","tid":633083,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}